sentences: A Boston native, Brain started his music production company, Underground Productions, Inc. in 1992, in collaboration with Brad Young.
Most recently, he produced and recorded UK pop vocalist Lauren Bennettâ€™s vocal for the LMFAO hit Party Rock Anthem, which became a number 1 hit on the Billboard pop charts.
Brain has produced five RIAA certified Platinum and Gold albums and singles, including a Platinum single for the number-one selling song Summer Girls, recorded by LFO on Arista Records.
